# **Project 4: Cloud Cost & Security Dashboard**

```markdown
# Cloud Cost & Security Dashboard

## Overview
Dashboard to track cloud costs, unused resources, and security compliance across AWS & GCP. Demonstrates strategic thinking, governance, and multi-cloud operational excellence.

## Tech Stack
- Backend: Node.js / Python (data collection)
- Frontend: React.js
- Terraform (IaC for dashboard infra)
- Cloud APIs: AWS & GCP
- Visualization: Grafana / React Dashboard

## Features
- Tracks cloud spend and resource utilization
- Identifies security issues (IAM, encryption, public resources)
- Visualizes multi-cloud resources & compliance metrics
- Infrastructure provisioning via Terraform

## Architecture Diagram
![Architecture Diagram](./docs/architecture.png)

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repository
2. Install backend dependencies
